# Speckit 使用规范

- Speckit plan documents will remain in Chinese only; no new bilingual versions will be created.
- The directory structure for plans is fixed as `plans/<plan>/`.
- Each plan consists of `plan.md`, `spec.md`, `tasks.md`, and `constitution.md`.
- README and QUICKSTART files will remain bilingual (Chinese and English) as user documentation.
- When adding a new plan, update the references in the README; existing bilingual Speckit documents must be marked as deprecated.